quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  103,1,"Alla woondiri e waqtu takkusaan."
  103,2,"Pellet aade woni ko ustaare e halkaare."
  103,3,"Si wonah ɓeen goonɗiɓe ngolli ko moƴƴi, ɓe mbasandiri goonga, e muñal e dow goonga, ko sifariiɓe nih ndaɗata e nguurndam mum en aduna e laakara."
  104,1,"Halkaare e lepte cattuɗe woodanii ño*oowo ko heewi e juwoowo aade en."
  104,2,"Oon mbo woni himme makko ko renndinde ngalu e limde mbo, o alah himme goo."
  104,3,"Hombo sikka jawdi makko ndi o renndini ndi danndat mo e maayde, o wuura e aduna haa pooma."
  104,4,"Alah wonah no majjuɓe mbaadiniri nih, ma ɓe mbedde e yiite jahannama heltatnge kala ko wedda e henge sabu sattude bone mannge."
  104,5,"Hol mbo anndin Ma-aan nelaaɗo- ngee yiite heltoowe kala ko weddaa e mannge?"
  104,6,"Konge yiite Alla huɓɓatnge."
  104,7,"Ngeen yiite woni yulatnge keeñ."
  104,8,"Ngeen de konge sokaange e dow leptateeɓe ɓe."
  104,9,"E doosɗe poottiɗe juutɗe haa gooto waawatah yaltude."
  105,1,"Mbela a anndah-aan nelaaɗo- no Alla waɗi Abraha e wondiiɓe mum jom en ñiiwo ndeɓe faalano yirbinde Kaaba."
  105,2,"Ko goongo Alla waɗii pehe mum en bonɗe yirbinde Kaaba ko pertuɗe, ɓe ndañaani faale mum en falaade yimɓe ɓe Kaaba ɓe ndañaani heen hay huunde."
  105,3,"O neli e mum en ndiwri ndi ardi dente dente."
  105,4,"Hondi werlooɓe kaaƴe loope joorɗe."
  105,5,"Alla waɗi ɓe hono kaakooli ɗi daabe ñaami ɗi njaɓɓi ɗi."